              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "1CANTMF"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Measurement was carried out at ISAC2",
                "facility at TRIUMF. Cyclotron was used to produce",
                "radioactive 9Li beam."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "LINAC"
                ],
                "institute": "1CANTMF"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Radioactive 9Li beam was accelerated",
                "to desired energy by RFQ and linear accelerator. Stable",
                " 7Li beam was produced in local ion source and",
                "accelerated in the same RF system."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " An array of 18 (300mm**2) Si detectors",
                "surrounding the target was used to detect decay alpha",
                "particles emitted from evaporation residues that",
                "stopped in the Pb/Bi targets in the beam-off period.",
                "The geometrical efficiency of the array for detecting",
                "decay alpha particles emitted by the evaporation",
                "residues that stopped in the targets was evaluated",
                "by a Monte Carlo simulation to be 20%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "ASPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Proton beams (500 MeV) with an intensity of 70 mu-A",
                "struck Ta metal production targets. Beams of",
                "radioactive 9Li were extracted with energies up to",
                "18.4 keV, mass-separated by passage through two",
                "dipole magnets, and accelerated to their final",
                "energy by radiofrequency quadrupole and drift-tube",
                "linear accelerators. The stable 7Li beam used to",
                "calibrate the efficiency of the experimental setup",
                " (sub. 7,8,9) was generated using a local ion source."
              ]
            }
          ],
